es in soil. Many people know about it from the 2001 <a href="https://medlineplus.gov/biodefenseandbioterrorism.html">bioterror</a> attacks. In the attacks, someone purposely spread anthrax through the U.S. mail. This killed five people and made 22 sick. </p>
