<p>With bone marrow disease, there are problems with the stem cells or how they develop:</p>
<ul>
	<li>In <a href="https://medlineplus.gov/leukemia.html">leukemia</a>, a cancer of the blood, the bone marrow makes abnormal white blood cells</li>
