</a>, or <a href="https://medlineplus.gov/radiationexposure.html">radiation</a>. Scalds from hot liquids and steam, building fires and flammable liquids and gases are the most common causes of burns. Another kind is an <a href="https://medlineplus.gov/inhalationinjuries.html">inhalation injury</a>, caused by breathing smoke.</p>
