	<a href="https://medlineplus.gov/childbirth.html">Childbirth</a> is the process of giving birth to a baby. It includes labor and delivery. Usually everything goes well, but problems can happen. They may cause a risk to the mother, baby, or both. Some of the more common childbirth problems include:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
